* This is a Spring Boot application set up using Spring Initializer using Maven and Spring Web dependencies.
* The application demonstrates how to build different APIs. The APIs allow the creation of an employee management sytem.
* The APIs perform CRUD.

User story

As a user, I want to be able to Create, Read, Update and Delete a user from postman or any other API building platform.
Then when I refresh the browser, the changes are reflected on the browser as well.
